survey_response.review_text: Dr. Sandeep and his staff are warm, professional , and made me feel extremely cared for throughout my time with them. It’s very clear that Dr. Sandeep is very experienced and knowledgeable. He explained all the treatment and the Process very nicely. My Root Canal treatment was done very properly. He does advise and answers all my Question or concerns.I always had a fear when it comes to Visit a Dentist. But this was the best experience, and all my fear were washed away. It was a Pain less process for which I am very Grateful to Him.There is no other dentist I would go to or recommend! When you find the best, you keep it!  A big Thank you to him and his team for the great work.

Doctor was very cordial in his attitude
Gave personal attention n tested me for root Canal
I am fully satisfied with his treatment
His assistance were also very cordial in their behaviour.
Premises n equipments kept very clean n neat
I will recommend d doctor to my friends, relatives n
well wishers.

Sandeep,
A gentle giant, he has the knack to calm treat the client however hyper / anxious sounds he/she. I have been visiting him since he started his practice, one knows with him the "crown's safe".

Visiting once you don't need to look back for years, not many dentists maintain this side of the ethical practices, 

P.S. It's a package deal You get 2 expert for the price of 1 his wife also an M.D. both refer and discuss the client with equal profession and empathy.

Well i sincerely do not have words to express my satisfaction i felt at this clinic....the ever smiling and calm duo.....Dr. Sandeep and Dr. Jyotsna....they are more like a friend than a dentist.... well that doesnt mean they arent good dentists....the thing that makes them different than other professionals is their empathy towards patients....the comfort zone they create so that even the most painful of the procedures feel painless....hats off to you two.... and other doctors as well

I did RCT in this clinic a year ago. * ********** **** **** ****** *** *** ******** *** ******** **** ******This doctor was hesitating to give a bill to me. He was behaving extremely rude with patients and his co-workers. i was asking for bill from him everyday but he was keep on pushing it for another day then at last day he took 500 rs. extra from me saying it was cavity in my tooth. 
Never visit this clinic. ********* ** **** ****** ** ******** ** ***** ********

My fillings were't well treated. On first meeting he said I have 3 cavities; surprisingly which increased to 4 in my next visit. 
**** ******** ****** ***** Now i have regular problem of food getting stuck in those teeth. 

Also i was charged 200 Rs for consultation fess while on Practo they mentioned only 100 Rs.

Experience was really good. Happy with overall treatment. Explaining the actual problem and the required treatment before actually starting it. Important is the Dr did not just rush into things she gave me enough time to think.
From my experience I found that both Mr and Mrs Patel are very professional. 

Only one thing I would like to suggest is there is constant conversation between the two ..which sometime doesn't go well with the patients. Else its a 4/5 for me as a experience and I would definitely recommend to others.
